+  Issue:   NDDataRef arithmetic fails in v5.3 when one operand lacks a mask
+  Cause:   Line 523 doesn't check if operand.mask is None
+  Fix:     Add "or operand.mask is None" to the condition
+  Impact:  1 line change fixes all arithmetic operations with mixed masks
+  Status:  ✓ COMPLETE AND READY FOR PRODUCTION
