+  File: astropy/nddata/mixins/ndarithmetic.py
+  Line: 523
+  
+  FROM: elif operand is None:
+  TO:   elif operand is None or operand.mask is None:
+
+THAT'S IT! One condition added prevents passing None to mask functions.
