+WHY THIS MATTERS:
+================================================================================
+
+Data reduction in astronomy requires tracking different types of bad pixels:
+  - Saturated pixels (one bit flag)
+  - Non-linear pixels (different bit flag)
+  - Unilluminated pixels (yet another bit flag)
